---
import Phones from '../assets/images/phones.png';
import Stars from '../assets/images/stars.png';
---

<section class="section-shell py-16 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-[1700px] mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1.12fr)] gap-12 md:gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-155 text-center md:text-left">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-200">
        <span class="inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-trueview-blue to-trueview-red"></span>
        #1 trusted source for lab-tested supplements
      </span>

      <h2 class="mt-6 md:mt-7 text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-[64px] font-bold leading-[1.06] md:leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.03em] md:tracking-[-0.035em]">
        Supplements don’t regulate
        <br />
        themselves, <span class="text-trueview-red">so we do!</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 md:mt-8 text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl leading-[1.55] max-w-130 mx-auto md:mx-0">
        Reading lab reports shouldn’t turn into a full-time job.
        We translate complex data into Pass/Fails-covering accuracy, heavy metals,
        and microbes - just verify into your fingertips.
      </p>

      <a href="/waitlist" class="mt-8 md:mt-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-[#2f6bff] to-[#1f49e8] px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/30 transition hover:brightness-110">
        Join the waitlist
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="relative min-h-[360px] sm:min-h-[480px] md:min-h-280 overflow-visible">
      <img
        src={Stars.src}
        width={Stars.width}
        height={Stars.height}
        alt="Decorative stars"
        class="pointer-events-none select-none absolute left-1/2 top-0 z-0 w-[320px] max-w-none -translate-x-1/2 sm:w-[440px] md:left-auto md:right-0 md:top-0 md:w-200 md:translate-x-0"
      />
      <img
        src={Phones.src}
        width={Phones.width}
        height={Phones.height}
        alt="Vista previa de la app trueview en varios teléfonos"
        class="pointer-events-none select-none absolute left-1/2 -top-8 z-10 w-[360px] max-w-none -translate-x-1/2 sm:w-[500px] md:h-[1500px] sm:-top-16 md:left-auto md:-right-20 md:-top-40 md:w-200 md:translate-x-0"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
